---
/** Labeled compound-interest formula matching the methodology copy. */
---

<figure class="content-figure data-figure">
  <div class="fig-inner" role="img" aria-label="Formula A equals P times open parenthesis 1 plus r over n close parenthesis to the power of n times t">
    <p class="fig-title">Discrete compounding formula</p>
    <div class="formula-box">
      <span class="main">A = P × (1 + r/n)<sup>n×t</sup></span>
    </div>
    <div class="legend">
      <div><span class="k">A</span><span>Maturity (final) balance</span></div>
      <div><span class="k">P</span><span>Principal — starting deposit</span></div>
      <div><span class="k">r</span><span>Annual nominal rate (decimal)</span></div>
      <div><span class="k">n</span><span>Compounds per year (e.g. 365 daily)</span></div>
      <div><span class="k">t</span><span>Time in years (months ÷ 12)</span></div>
    </div>
    <p class="note">
      Continuous form: <code>A = P × e<sup>r×t</sup></code>. When you enter APY, Nestfigure converts it to the
      matching nominal <code>r</code> for your compounding choice.
    </p>
  </div>
  <figcaption>Standard retail CD math used by the Nestfigure CD calculator.</figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
  .fig-inner {
    padding: 20px;
  }
  .fig-title {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-graphite);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }
  .formula-box {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f0f5fe 0%, #ffffff 100%);
    border: 1px solid #c9daf8;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 20px 16px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .main {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: clamp(16px, 3.5vw, 22px);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .legend {
    display: grid;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .legend div {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 36px 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-iron);
  }
  .k {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: #f0f5fe;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-pale-slate);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-cobalt);
  }
  .note {
    margin: 14px 0 0;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--color-graphite);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .note code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    background: #f0f5fe;
    padding: 1px 5px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
</style>
